@node CMD_MOVE "MOVE"

   @{b}NAME@{ub}
       MOVE

   @{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub} 
       MOVE

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub} 
       Move selected files from one filesection to another filesection.
       Both sections have to be properly set before you call this
       function (as when you use MOVE button).       

